      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-tit-pgm-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase video                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ER"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattini a linea 01                             *
