      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-ord-rof           not  = 02
                     go to tdo-ric-sel-120.
           if        rr-dcn-max           =    zero
                     go to tdo-ric-sel-120.
           if        rr-dcn-min           not  > rr-dcn-max
                     go to tdo-ric-sel-120.
           move      "Data consegna richiesta massima inferiore a quella
      -              " minima !      "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           go to     tdo-ric-sel-900.
       tdo-ric-sel-120.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     tdo-ric-sel-999.
       tdo-ric-sel-900.
